 GEOSPHERE CAPITAL Overview



												   Geosphere Capital Management Ll is a hedge fund that manages 184.7 MM dollars in regulatory AUM and has 9 employees, of which 4 perform investment advisory functions. The manager's has disclosed holdings from 12/31/07 to 03/31/17. The fund's latest filing disclosed 81MM in positions, representing 44% of the manager's regulatory AUM.
												



