GeoSphere Capital Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 7:33 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of GeoSphere Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
GeoSphere Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to other investment advisors. The firm invests in the public equity and hedging markets across the globe. It employs fundamental, technical, and qualitative analysis to make its investments. The firm seeks to invest in the stocks of companies in natural resources and industrials sectors. GeoSphere Capital Management, LLC was founded in July 2007 and is based in New York City.


747 3rd Avenue26th FloorNew York, NY 10022United StatesFounded in 2007



Phone: 212-616-1100

Fax: 212-616-1101








