Geosphere Capital Management Has Boosted Its Noble Plc (NE) Position; 4 Analysts Bullish PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (PTCT)


					

						July 25, 2017 - By marketbeat

Among 8 analysts covering PTC Therapeutics (NASDAQ:PTCT), 4 have Buy rating, 0 Sell and 4 Hold. Therefore 50% are positive. PTC Therapeutics had 22 analyst reports since July 31, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. RBC Capital Markets maintained the shares of PTCT in report on Wednesday, July 5 with “Hold” rating. The company was maintained on Wednesday, February 24 by Wedbush. The stock of PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT) has “Sector Perform” rating given on Friday, November 11 by RBC Capital Markets. The stock has “Neutral” rating by JP Morgan on Tuesday, February 23. The stock has “Underperform” rating by Jefferies on Wednesday, November 25. Oppenheimer maintained PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT) on Friday, October 16 with “Outperform” rating. RBC Capital Markets downgraded PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT) rating on Wednesday, February 24. RBC Capital Markets has “Sector Perform” rating and $11 target. Citigroup downgraded the stock to “Neutral” rating in Wednesday, February 24 report. The rating was maintained by RBC Capital Markets on Friday, October 16 with “Outperform”. As per Monday, November 14, the company rating was upgraded by Credit Suisse. See PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT) latest ratings:
05/07/2017 Broker: RBC Capital Markets Rating: Hold New Target: $12.0000 Maintain30/06/2017 Broker: Cowen & Co Rating: Hold Maintain07/06/2017 Broker: Citigroup Rating: Buy New Target: $18.0000 






Geosphere Capital Management increased Noble Corp Plc (NE) stake by 112.5% reported in 2016Q4 SEC filing. Geosphere Capital Management acquired 225,000 shares as Noble Corp Plc (NE)’s stock declined 34.72%. The Geosphere Capital Management holds 425,000 shares with $2.52 million value, up from 200,000 last quarter. Noble Corp Plc now has $971.40 million valuation. The stock increased 3.27% or $0.13 during the last trading session, reaching $4.1. About 6.05M shares traded. Noble Corporation Ordinary Shares (UK) (NYSE:NE) has declined 46.66% since July 25, 2016 and is downtrending. It has underperformed by 63.36% the S&P500.
Since May 23, 2017, it had 1 buy, and 0 selling transactions for $337,230 activity. The insider Svoronos Dawn bought 25,000 shares worth $337,230.
Investors sentiment decreased to 0.93 in Q4 2016. Its down 0.07, from 1 in 2016Q3. It worsened, as 19 investors sold PTC Therapeutics, Inc. shares while 40 reduced holdings. 25 funds opened positions while 30 raised stakes. 27.52 million shares or 2.54% less from 28.23 million shares in 2016Q3 were reported. Everpoint Asset Mngmt Limited Liability Co accumulated 10,000 shares or 0% of the stock. Great West Life Assurance Can invested in 0% or 4,580 shares. The Denmark-based Cam Gp Holdings A S has invested 0.03% in PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT). Oppenheimer & reported 48,160 shares. Morgan Stanley has invested 0% in PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT). Fmr Ltd holds 732,044 shares. Employees Retirement Association Of Colorado invested in 0% or 8,019 shares. Blackrock Mgmt Llc invested 0% of its portfolio in PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT). Fisher Asset Mgmt Limited Liability Corp stated it has 87,842 shares or 0% of all its holdings. The New York-based Prelude Cap Mngmt Ltd Com has invested 0.24% in PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT). Tocqueville Asset Management L P has 0.11% invested in PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT) for 785,975 shares. Cubist Systematic Strategies Lc holds 0.01% in PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT) or 14,689 shares. Blackrock owns 0% invested in PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT) for 51,013 shares. Numeric Ltd Liability Company accumulated 0.06% or 555,819 shares. Tower Rech Ltd Liability Company (Trc) stated it has 5,510 shares or 0.01% of all its holdings.
PTC Therapeutics, Inc. is a biopharmaceutical company. The company has market cap of $876.79 million. The Firm is focused on the discovery, development and commercialization of medicines using its expertise in ribonucleic acid biology. It currently has negative earnings. The Company’s product pipeline includes Ataluren (Translarna), PTC596 and RG7916.
The stock decreased 1.86% or $0.4 during the last trading session, reaching $21.15. About 455,119 shares traded. PTC Therapeutics, Inc. (NASDAQ:PTCT) has risen 104.51% since July 25, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 87.81% the S&P500.
Among 32 analysts covering Noble Corp PLC (NYSE:NE), 8 have Buy rating, 8 Sell and 16 Hold. Therefore 25% are positive. Noble Corp PLC had 72 analyst reports since July 31, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The stock of Noble Corporation Ordinary Shares (UK) (NYSE:NE) earned “Hold” rating by Jefferies on Wednesday, September 28. On Friday, February 5 the stock rating was maintained by Howard Weil with “Sector Outperform”. On Monday, October 3 the stock rating was downgraded by Societe Generale to “Hold”. The rating was initiated by Howard Weil with “Sector Perform” on Wednesday, September 14. The stock of Noble Corporation Ordinary Shares (UK) (NYSE:NE) has “Hold” rating given on Friday, March 24 by Tudor Pickering. As per Wednesday, September 21, the company rating was upgraded by Goldman Sachs. RBC Capital Markets maintained the stock with “Sell” rating in Thursday, July 20 report. The rating was upgraded by Barclays Capital on Monday, January 9 to “Equal Weight”. The stock of Noble Corporation Ordinary Shares (UK) (NYSE:NE) earned “Underweight” rating by Simmons & Co on Friday, March 11. As per Friday, October 7, the company rating was downgraded by Seaport Global Securities.
Geosphere Capital Management decreased Forum Energy Technologies In (NYSE:FET) stake by 42,300 shares to 157,700 valued at $3.47 million in 2016Q4. It also reduced Continental Resources Inc (NYSE:CLR) stake by 30,000 shares and now owns 60,000 shares. Diamondback Energy Inc (NASDAQ:FANG) was reduced too. 



